Format: As a [user role], I want to [do something with the system]

As a user, I want to upload local audio file and put it into my playlist.
As a user, I want to sort playlist by name alphabet.
As a user, I want to sort playlist by modified date.
As a user, I want to sort playlist randomly by clicking the Sort random button.
As a user, I want to upload media through URL and add the downloaded audio into my playlist.
As a user, I want duplicate upload handling so I can choose to replace, rename, or cancel.
As a user, I want to rename a song from the playlist.
As a user, I want to delete a song from the playlist with a confirmation step.
As a user, I want to open the selected song location in File Explorer.
As a user, I want to click a song in the playlist and play it.
As a user, I want to pause and resume playback using the playback control button.
As a user, I want to go to previous and next song from the playback controls.
As a user, I want the next song to auto-play when the current song ends.
As a user, I want to seek through the song using a progress slider.
As a user, I want to see current time and total duration while a song is playing.
As a user, I want to control system output volume using the main volume slider.
As a user, I want to set and save a separate volume level for each song.
As a user, I want to refresh and sync playlist items with files in my local playlist folder.
As a user, I want my playlist metadata and last selected song index to persist after reopening the app.